Program: Omnibus
Title: Beards
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p0376k5v
Last Broadcast Date: 15 August 1991
A look at the history of beards, the meanings we ascribe to them and the religious symbolism of facial hair within different religions. Contributors include Leslie Dunkling who has written a book on beards. Picture: Bearded man, Credit: Thinkstock